Download here: http://zune.elxx.net/

Just a quick little app I threw together on my Zune HD today. Draw with your finger(s), shake to clear the screen. It's a shame that MS has no plans of giving us a way to distribute these apps & games.

This uses the just recently released XNA Game Studio 3.1 Zune Extensions:
http://forums.xna.com/forums/t/38975.aspx

